00:04:10.974 --> 00:04:13.052
A young master like you
taking care of me?

00:04:13.053 --> 00:04:15.093
You must've been
trying to take advantage of me

00:04:15.094 --> 00:04:15.892
and get close to me

00:04:15.893 --> 00:04:16.933
while I was hurt.

00:04:16.934 --> 00:04:17.813
Ridiculous.

00:04:18.134 --> 00:04:19.732
Anyone seeing us together

00:04:19.733 --> 00:04:21.253
would think you're the one trying

00:04:21.254 --> 00:04:22.573
to take advantage of me.

00:04:22.574 --> 00:04:23.294
You...

00:04:24.334 --> 00:04:25.292
You're a man.

00:04:25.293 --> 00:04:26.052
A male.

00:04:26.053 --> 00:04:27.534
Males are men.

00:04:27.613 --> 00:04:29.692
A man out in the world needs to respect

00:04:29.693 --> 00:04:30.933
and value himself.

00:04:39.774 --> 00:04:42.534
