00:04:44.613 --> 00:04:46.534
All thanks to my care, of course.

00:04:55.974 --> 00:04:58.133
The Yang poison in you
has eased up a lot too.

00:04:59.334 --> 00:05:00.333
Did you secretly

00:05:00.334 --> 00:05:01.654
take the medicine last night?

00:05:03.094 --> 00:05:04.453
Last night?

00:05:05.574 --> 00:05:06.692
I just held you as we slept.

00:05:06.693 --> 00:05:07.933
Stop it.

00:05:10.613 --> 00:05:12.654
Why is this sigil still on my hand?

00:05:12.774 --> 00:05:14.492
When will it come off?

00:05:14.493 --> 00:05:15.812
I have to admit

00:05:15.813 --> 00:05:17.373
that you did save my life.

00:05:17.454 --> 00:05:19.213
Until I get the sigil back,

00:05:19.214 --> 00:05:20.854
you can be my servant.

00:05:23.293 --> 00:05:24.334
What?

00:05:24.534 --> 00:05:26.414
Me? Your servant?

00:05:26.894 --> 00:05:28.252
You're at my place now.

00:05:28.253 --> 00:05:29.732
I saved your life.

00:05:29.733 --> 00:05:30.692
It makes more sense

00:05:30.693 --> 00:05:32.094
for you to be my servant.

00:05:32.133 --> 00:05:33.133
Besides,

00:05:33.534 --> 00:05:35.654
your treasure is still on my hand.

00:05:36.813 --> 00:05:38.252
From what I see,

00:05:38.253 --> 00:05:39.414
this sigil

00:05:39.654 --> 00:05:41.133
has a mind of its own.

00:05:41.414 --> 00:05:43.372
It ended up on my hand

00:05:43.373 --> 00:05:45.053
under some special circumstances.

00:05:45.534 --> 00:05:48.013
If you want to get it back,

00:05:48.373 --> 00:05:49.813
you need to do me a favor.

00:05:50.373 --> 00:05:52.174
Take me to Wujing City.

00:05:52.454 --> 00:05:54.172
That place is huge.

00:05:54.173 --> 00:05:55.492
I'm sure we can find a way

00:05:55.493 --> 00:05:56.773
to get this sigil off.

00:05:56.774 --> 00:05:58.453
Just go wherever you want.

00:05:58.454 --> 00:06:00.053
Why should I help you?

00:06:00.854 --> 00:06:02.333
Ladies from the Feng family

00:06:02.334 --> 00:06:03.453
