00:06:06.813 --> 00:06:08.214
So...

00:06:09.253 --> 00:06:10.573
Help me with a little act.

00:06:10.574 --> 00:06:12.053
Pretend to be my husband.

00:06:12.214 --> 00:06:14.292
That way, I can leave this place.

00:06:14.293 --> 00:06:15.492
No way.

00:06:15.493 --> 00:06:17.372
I knew you were cold-hearted,

00:06:17.373 --> 00:06:18.252
only taking,

00:06:18.253 --> 00:06:19.373
never giving.

00:06:19.534 --> 00:06:20.612
Fine, don't help.

00:06:20.613 --> 00:06:21.612
I'll go to my uncle.

00:06:21.613 --> 00:06:23.053
He'll surely have a way.

00:06:25.493 --> 00:06:26.573
You.

00:06:27.454 --> 00:06:28.692
Stay right here.

00:06:28.693 --> 00:06:29.894
Don't go out.

00:06:55.574 --> 00:06:57.453
Dragon God, hear my prayers.

00:06:57.774 --> 00:06:59.252
I am Feng Zhilou.

00:06:59.253 --> 00:07:01.372
Dragon God, please help me

00:07:01.373 --> 00:07:03.172
leave Feng Manor soon

00:07:03.173 --> 00:07:04.854
and make a name for myself.

00:07:05.534 --> 00:07:08.172
Without a spiritual root,

00:07:08.173 --> 00:07:09.612
I can't cultivate martial arts

00:07:09.613 --> 00:07:11.053
or fight upfront,

00:07:11.293 --> 00:07:12.013
