00:07:12.014 --> 00:07:13.573
I can heal the wounded

00:07:13.574 --> 00:07:15.654
behind the lines.

00:07:16.094 --> 00:07:17.612
Dragon God, please

00:07:17.613 --> 00:07:18.933
