00:15:04.934 --> 00:15:07.534
and keeps covering for Feng Zhilou.

00:15:07.653 --> 00:15:09.134
If this keeps up,

00:15:09.253 --> 00:15:11.973
not only will the Lenghou family
look down on us,

00:15:12.174 --> 00:15:13.372
but everyone in the world

00:15:13.373 --> 00:15:15.494
will laugh at us.

00:15:15.694 --> 00:15:16.774
By then,

00:15:16.854 --> 00:15:19.174
how can we do business

00:15:19.214 --> 00:15:21.534
or stand our ground in the world?

00:15:21.653 --> 00:15:23.733
That disgraceful woman

00:15:24.294 --> 00:15:27.093
needs to be punished
according to family rules.

00:15:28.413 --> 00:15:29.853
Drown her.

00:15:30.214 --> 00:15:31.733
Make an example out of her.

00:15:31.893 --> 00:15:34.573
Get rid of this shame in our family

00:15:34.694 --> 00:15:37.374
and have Yunqiao marry
into the Lenghou family

00:15:37.493 --> 00:15:39.014
to seal the alliance.

00:15:57.373 --> 00:15:58.494
Father,

00:15:59.253 --> 00:16:01.134
I made you some soup.

00:16:07.893 --> 00:16:09.254
(Father,)

00:16:09.574 --> 00:16:12.294
(get a good night's sleep tomorrow.)

00:16:18.733 --> 00:16:21.012
The second daughter of the Feng family,

00:16:21.013 --> 00:16:22.254
Feng Zhilou,

00:16:22.773 --> 00:16:24.813
is already betrothed

00:16:24.934 --> 00:16:27.973
but shamelessly involved
with a foreign man,

00:16:27.974 --> 00:16:29.693
ruining the family's reputation.

00:16:29.694 --> 00:16:31.492
Her sins are grave.

00:16:31.493 --> 00:16:33.654
She must be executed.

00:16:34.773 --> 00:16:36.774
Drown Feng Zhilou in the pond.

00:16:44.800 --> 00:16:50.574
♪Like petals fall, gone with the clouds♪

00:16:50.575 --> 00:16:56.570
♪Like stars fade fast in open skies♪

00:16:56.687 --> 00:17:02.386
♪Like snowflakes melting softly
in the evening haze♪

00:17:02.387 --> 00:17:08.711
♪Like your fleeting glance
that gave me one brief dream's grace♪

00:17:08.712 --> 00:17:14.645
♪Like fireflies flicker
through wild grass, fleeting light♪

00:17:14.812 --> 00:17:20.382
♪Like evening breeze
that stirs soft hair in twilight♪

00:17:20.662 --> 00:17:26.386
♪Like fleeting thoughts
that surge and then unwind♪

00:17:26.387 --> 00:17:32.324
♪Chance meetings fade,
just empty rooms left behind♪

00:17:32.325 --> 00:17:37.957
♪You brought a wave
that stirred a wild, restless sea♪

00:17:38.237 --> 00:17:44.132
♪Light as a feather,
yet it sank an island deep in me♪

00:17:44.312 --> 00:17:50.870
♪In that one moment,
life's grip I couldn't break or sway♪

00:17:50.875 --> 00:17:56.632
♪Leaving me lost in memories,
small and fading away♪